in python make a plot that compares two columns in a dataframe.
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt 
from pandas import DataFrame, Series  
  
# create sample data frame  
data = {'column1': [10,20,30], 'column2':[5,8,9]} 
df = DataFrame(data)   
  
# plot the columns  
plt.plot(df['column1'], df['column2']) 
plt.show()
